	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64893437"><p>An accurate headline, for a change. In fact, we don't know where the tipping points are.</p><p>This is a real problem. Should we worry about worst case scenarios when we don't know when, exactly, they get triggered?</p><p>Another thing to note is that we don't really know for sure what the effect of the AMOC on European climate is. This is still debated.  (Good article here, though: <a href="https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/sciadv.aaz4876" title="science.org">https://www.science.org/doi/10...</a> [science.org] )</p></div>
